{"type":"answer","id":56543,"parentType":"question","parentId":9181,"uid":11512,"contents":"撇開歸屬，有可能會造成局勢更加危險<br>\n以台灣為例，每次拍到那面旗子中共都會打馬賽克抹掉或是藝人舉旗就砲轟<br>\n這嚴重威脅到中共的政權正當性<br>\n國共本一家，現在它對中國國民黨如此推崇是因為它們早就不反共了<br>\n還要幫著中共侵略台灣呢(和平協議)<br>\n本土派也不喜歡那面旗子沒錯，那就是黨國不分的最佳證明<br>\n如果只有學過中華民國史沒有學過台灣本史的<br>\n建議可以透過一點動畫入門來瞭解<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLwItru4bLdHwtl3sB6n3I_sIMk77_n1Ce\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLwItru4bLdHwtl3sB6n3I_sIMk77_n1Ce</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLMKjXukzK9Ochx1-etY5Yr-y0-zGO9cpk\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLMKjXukzK9Ochx1-etY5Yr-y0-zGO9cpk</a><br>\n中國國民黨針對轉型正義與受難者家屬的嘴臉<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1843085912407834\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1843085912407834</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10untrusted fake 2049bbsrmalink.php?story_fbid=10220220408397369&amp;id=1142107210</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\" url=\"\" img=\"\" ahr0chm6ly9plmltz3vylmnvbs9tvhm3am1rlmpwzw\"=\"\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/STs7jmk.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/STs7jmk.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/K1cI67E.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K1cI67E.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/K1cI67E.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/FqcaJjV.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FqcaJjV.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/FqcaJjV.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/sLeheOo.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sLeheOo.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/sLeh